        "x": -220,
        "y": -460
      },
      "width": 540,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bootstrap Tutorial\n\nUse the onboarding guide and toolbar handoff to initialize your chatbot, then return to a clean graph.\n\n1. Open the onboarding guide.\n2. Use the toolbar onboarding button to copy the handoff.\n3. Paste the chatbot's JSON response back into Twilite.\n4. Start from a blank graph once the handshake succeeds."
      }
    },
